-- Emirates Selects GE, United Technologies Venture for A380 Engine Contract
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-07-19T10:52:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/emirates-selects-ge-united-technologies-venture-for-a380-engine-contract.html

          
          
             Emirates, the largest Arab airline,
said it selected GP7200 engines from Engine Alliance to power
its 32 Airbus A380 aircraft ordered last month. The total value
of the agreement, including spare engines, is about $4.8 billion
over the life of the contract, it said in an e-mailed statement
today.   
